Fractal — Cognitive Fractal
===========================

This is an original implementation. It does not bundle or redistribute
any third-party source code.

Runtime dependencies (system tools, not distributed with this plugin):
  - node (>= 18)
  - ripgrep (optional; falls back to system grep when absent)

History
-------
Early versions (v2) used tree-sitter + sqlite-wasm to build a code graph
and borrowed language extractors from CodeGraph (MIT). That approach was
abandoned — the current version uses "live agent retrieval (ripgrep) +
semantic memory (.nav/)". No third-party borrowed code remains.
The v2 implementation is preserved in git history for reference.
